# Backend Course Repository

Welcome to my backend course repository on GitHub.

This repository contains solutions to my assignments and projects that were delivered to my instructor or mentor throughout the backend course. The goal is to keep my work organized, readable, and easy to review.

## Overview

This repo includes:
- Assignment solutions
- Project implementations


## Structure

- Assignments/ — Assignment-n for course assignments
- Course Application/ application-related files
- Projects/
## Purpose

The purpose of this repository is to:
- document my learning journey
- showcase my backend development progress
- provide a clean record of completed work

